3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper proposes a decentralized scheme for transforming the interaction graph of a multi-agent network, which is related to networking and internet architecture.

5. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper proposes a decentralized scheme for transforming the interaction graph of a multi-agent network, which is related to distributed computing.
